  <h1 class="show-title">AI Atlas browse — two directions</h1>
  <p class="show-deck">Two compact takes on the AI Atlas browse map. Six archetypes, named definition, one nearby neighbor, 1–2 differentiators each, and a single obvious route to the AI Field Guide. Same paper, ink and accents as the rest of the product.</p>

