                <div class="scen"><div class="ttl">Concentration tightens</div><div class="meta">Frontier capability narrows to fewer labs.</div></div>
                <div class="scen"><div class="ttl">Open weights win</div><div class="meta">Open releases set the deployment baseline.</div></div>
