          <p class="summary">Foundation places you in the rules-and-institutions liberal family with constructivist overlap. Three modules later, two lanes have moved meaningfully — competition and political economy — while the rest sit close to where they started. The chart below shows only the deviation: each bar is how far a lane moved, in which direction, and which module pulled it.</p>
