          <div class="row"><span class="k">Changed most</span><span class="v high">Competition lane · +1.8 toward competition</span></div>
          <div class="row"><span class="k">Stayed stable</span><span class="v stable">Oversight · Legitimacy</span></div>
        </aside>
      </div>

      <!-- The dominant visual -->
      <div class="d3-chart" role="img" aria-label="Five lanes showing deviation from baseline under module pressure">
        <div class="d3-chart-head">
          <span class="t">Deviation under module pressure</span>
          <div class="scale">
            <span class="l">← Toward coordination / institutions / restraint</span>
            <span class="c">Baseline</span>
            <span class="r">Toward competition / capability / autonomy →</span>
