    <span><span class="swatch med"></span>Medium — precision / polish</span>
    <span><span class="swatch low"></span>Low — nice-to-have</span>
    <span><span class="swatch struct"></span>Structural — scope-level</span>
  </div>

  <nav class="toc" aria-label="Contents">
